      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEAVENLY FLYER (2) has been competitive of late and kept the ball rolling last time when 5.5 metres from the winner in third over 2150m at Bendigo. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Won't find this any harder and she can take care of this line-up. ELLIANA (9) was out of the money two back at Kilmore. Turned in a better run last time out when second over 2190m at this track, beaten 8 metres. Can give this a mighty shake. HEYNOWHEYNOW (4) was easily accounted for when seventh over 2190m at this venue recently at his first race start. Strips fitter and can improve sharply. TOUCH OF REALITY (5) last appeared when third over 1690m here six months ago. Must be respected while fresh.",
